1
00:00:00,765 --> 00:00:05,030
Shall I make some coffee, Jane?
我来煮点咖啡好吗,Jane?
  
2
00:00:05,115 --> 00:00:08,992
That's a good idea, Charlotte.
这是个好主意,Charlotte.
  
3
00:00:09,170 --> 00:00:10,909
It's ready.
咖啡好了,
  
4
00:00:11,859 --> 00:00:14,747
Do you want any milk?
你要放点奶吗?
  
5
00:00:14,748 --> 00:00:17,523
Just a little, please.
请稍加一点.
  
6
00:00:17,524 --> 00:00:20,212
What about some sugar?
加些糖怎么样?
  
7
00:00:20,213 --> 00:00:22,814
Two teaspoonfuls?
两茶匙行吗?
  
8
00:00:23,023 --> 00:00:26,014
No, less than that.
不,再少一些.
  
9
00:00:26,015 --> 00:00:30,529
One and a half teaspoonfuls, please.
请放一勺儿半.
  
10
00:00:30,530 --> 00:00:33,088
That's enough for me.
那对我足够了.
  
11
00:00:33,709 --> 00:00:37,060
That was very nice.
太好了.
  
12
00:00:37,146 --> 00:00:39,807
Would you like some more?
你要再来点吗?
  
13
00:00:39,808 --> 00:00:42,570
Yes, please.
好的,请再来一点.
  
14
00:00:42,571 --> 00:00:46,166
I'd like a cigarette, too.
我还想抽枝烟.
  
15
00:00:46,426 --> 00:00:48,911
May I have one?
可以给我一枝吗?
  
16
00:00:49,084 --> 00:00:51,011
Of course.
当然可以.
  
17
00:00:51,367 --> 00:00:55,910
I think there are a few in that box.
我想那个盒子里有一些.
  
18
00:00:55,911 --> 00:00:58,515
I'm afraid it's empty.
我恐怕盒子是空的.
  
19
00:00:58,990 --> 00:01:01,086
What a pity!
真遗憾!
  
20
00:01:01,099 --> 00:01:03,384
It doesn't matter.
没关系.
  
21
00:01:03,582 --> 00:01:06,465
Have a biscuit instead.
那就吃块饼干吧.
  
22
00:01:06,767 --> 00:01:10,500
Eat more and smoke less!
多吃点,少抽点!
  
23
00:01:10,501 --> 00:01:13,500
That's very good advice!
这是极好的忠告啊!
  
